---
import MetricCard from "./MetricCard.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<section class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 pb-14 pt-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:pb-20 lg:pt-16">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Edge AI & Applied ML Lab Notebook</p>
    <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl">
      Yu Seungmin
      <span class="mt-3 block text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-700 sm:text-3xl">Edge AI & Applied Machine Learning Builder</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
      제한된 환경에서도 동작하는 경량 AI 모델과 현실 문제 해결형 머신러닝 파이프라인을 연구하고 구현합니다.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-muted">
      I build lightweight AI systems that turn complex real-world processes into measurable prediction problems.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href={`${base}research/`} class="rounded-md bg-ink px-5 py-3 text-sm font-black text-white shadow-soft transition hover:bg-accent">대표 연구 보기</a>
      <a href={`${base}resume/`} class="rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-black text-ink transition hover:border-accent hover:text-accent">이력서</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/ysmMachine" class="rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-black text-ink transition hover:border-accent hover:text-accent">GitHub</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-4">
      <MetricCard value="3" label="Papers" detail="Research outputs" />
      <MetricCard value="1" label="Journal" detail="Applied Sciences, 2025" />
      <MetricCard value="TOPCIT" label="Award" detail="National SW evaluation" />
      <MetricCard value="4.08" label="GPA" detail="4.5 scale" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-white shadow-soft">
    <div class="border-b border-line bg-white p-4">
      <img src={`${base}assets/papers/microforest-overview.png`} alt="MicroForest overview preview" class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1125px] object-contain" />
    </div>
    <div class="p-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Featured Evidence</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-black leading-tight text-ink">MicroForest: compact multi-task bottleneck prediction</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-muted">
        Baseline RFs -> SplitSelector -> Split Pool -> MTConstructor -> MicroForest. 여러 task별 Random Forest에서 핵심 split rule만 추출해 compact MicroTree ensemble로 재구성합니다.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line bg-paper p-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent">Compression</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-extrabold text-ink">Two orders smaller model size</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line bg-paper p-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-teal">Latency</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-extrabold text-ink">Up to 7.2x faster inference</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line bg-paper p-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent">Recall</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-extrabold text-ink">+34%p vs Random Forest</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line bg-paper p-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-teal">Scale</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-extrabold text-ink">Evaluated up to 150 tasks</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
